  "body": "<p>Some years ago, I attended one of Amy Tangerine’s workshops. It was 2015, I was in Barcelona with Amy Tangerine, and I had a wonderful time there.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ab9125130c975886.jpg?v=1782539540\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For this layout, I have used my favourite photo with Amy Tangerine, from the workshop back in Barcelona 2015. The photo has been printed as if it was a Polaroid, it is quite cool!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ffc0ae0176c38b6b.jpg?v=1782539543\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a78dd9c6fd334df2.jpg?v=1782539545\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I have used a yellow paper with “&amp;” in white as a base for the project. The color yellow is perfect! Moreover, I have glued a circle with flowers that I have cut with my Silhouette Cameo.</p><p>After that, I have added some different stickers with different designs and colors from some Amy Tangerine’s collections so I can decorate the layout with them.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a83708d544622adc.jpg?v=1782539549\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/edf36e6084001565.jpg?v=1782539551\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For the title of the project I have used a thickers alphabet from an old collection of Amy Tangerine and I have glued the word “Yessss” from the “Sunshine &amp; Good Times” collection from Amy Tangerine. What’s more, I have added different stickers with some sentences in gold. Gold color combines perfectly here!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d7b5ca0c1d4ae983.jpg?v=1782539554\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I have also put some puffy stickers from the collection “Sunshine &amp; Good Times” as other decorative elements on this layout.</p><p>I love how colorful and fun that this layout is. It is, no doubt, one of my favorites.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/50ebf3a879a7811b.jpg?v=1782539557\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>I am looking forward to going back to enjoy some of Amy’s workshops, I love her projects and her collections. In addition, she is a wonderful and funny person. Thanks Amy Tangerine for trusting in me to be a member of your design team. You are great!</p><p>Violeta Scrap</p><p><a href=\"http://violetascrap.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/violeta_scrap/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/violeta_scrap\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VioletaScrap/\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/VioletaScrap\">YouTube</a></p><p>Supplies: Sunshine &amp; Good Times - 12x12 Double Sided Paper - Be Happy (345702), Sunshine &amp; Good Times - Sticker Book (344862), Sunshine &amp; Good Times - Puffy Stickers (345712), Sunshine &amp; Good Times - Thickers - Let´s Dance (345713)</p><p><em>Thanks for sharing this layout with us, Violeta! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop Sunshine and Good Times at your local retailer or online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/sunshineandgoodtimes\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a> </p>"
